      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It truly breaks my heart to see this absolute gem go, but it\u2019s time for a new adventure. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and loved like a member of the family. It\u2019s in truly stunning, pristine condition; you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! There's one tiny, microscopic nick on the passenger door handle that you can't even see unless the light hits it just right, but otherwise, she's perfect. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is beautiful, come on over, let's have a chat, and I'll hand you the keys to your new favorite drive!",
